CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 13, 1954, pg. 12 reads: " More Queen Contestants - Another group of Pittsburgh teen-agers who are clamoring to wear the crown of Hill City Queen includes, left to right,...Shirley Davis...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Shirley Davis wearing striped shirt with dark collar and hoop earrings, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest
